getting you from clicking the

00:01:50.116 --> 00:01:51.556 A:middle
Capture button to into the

00:01:51.556 --> 00:01:52.946 A:middle
debugger much, much more

00:01:52.946 --> 00:01:53.256 A:middle
quickly.

