change on every single draw call

00:21:38.006 --> 00:21:39.726 A:middle
used in the pipeline, giving us

00:21:39.726 --> 00:21:41.296 A:middle
also whole space performance

00:21:41.296 --> 00:21:41.896 A:middle
improvements.

