00:28:30.766 --> 00:28:31.236 A:middle
caches.

00:28:31.966 --> 00:28:33.956 A:middle
Now that we have a better

00:28:33.956 --> 00:28:34.946 A:middle
understanding of the issue at

00:28:34.946 --> 00:28:36.966 A:middle
hand, let's focus on the

